# 🧠 Legal Mate Edge – Real-Time AI Legal Companion on NVIDIA Jetson

**Legal Mate Edge** is a cutting-edge GenAI-powered legal assistant that runs fully on-device using the **Gemma 3n LLM** and **NVIDIA Jetson** platform. It enables offline legal clause analysis, OCR-powered document scanning, and intelligent contract feedback—all in real-time on a portable, secure, and cost-efficient edge device.

![Banner](https://your-image-link.com/banner.png)

---

## 🚀 Key Features

✅ **Multimodal Interface**: Upload PDFs or images of legal documents  
✅ **On-Device Clause Extraction**: Run NLP + OCR analysis offline  
✅ **Privacy-First Legal AI**: No data leaves the device  
✅ **Voice & Visual Interaction**: Mic + camera input, speech + highlights output  
✅ **Realtime Feedback**: Flags risk, suggests edits, highlights missing clauses  

---

## 🔌 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech Used                                       |
|--------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| **LLM**      | Gemma 3n (3B) via Ollama on-device               |
| **OCR**      | Tesseract + EasyOCR                             |
| **Deployment**| NVIDIA Jetson Nano / Xavier NX                 |
| **Finetuning**| `unsloth` + QLoRA (efficient on-device tuning) |
| **Backend**  | FastAPI + TorchServe                             |
| **Frontend** | React + Streamlit + Firebase                    |

---

## 📍 Example Use Case

A field lawyer scans a printed NDA using the Jetson-powered Legal Mate Edge device at a remote location without internet. The device:

- Extracts clauses via OCR + NLP
- Flags missing indemnity terms
- Suggests rephrasing and redlines

All done **entirely offline**, safeguarding sensitive data and improving legal agility.

---

## 🧠 Why Gemma 3n?

We selected **Gemma 3n (3B)** for its:
- Lightweight architecture suitable for edge inference
- Open weights + privacy-first deployment
- Compatibility with `Ollama`, `GGUF`, and Jetson-optimized environments

---

## ⚙️ Architecture Overview

[ Jetson Device ] | [ Camera/Mic Input ] —> [ OCR (EasyOCR/Tesseract) ] | [ Legal PDF/Image ] —> [ FastAPI + TorchServe ] | [ Gemma 3n Inference ] —> [ Clause Detection + Feedback ] | [ React/Streamlit UI ] <—> [ Firebase Sync (optional) ]

